<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5820">أَبُو كُرَيْبٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1758">خَالِدُ بْنُ مَخْلَدٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5533">مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ جَعْفَرٍ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4473">الْعَلَاءِ بْنِ عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ مِثْلَهُ .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>